{
  "3296330": {
    "name": "时空策：湖",
    "steam_appid": 3296330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷失在这座漂浮于迷雾中的城市，追逐着力量与救赎的低语。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/e80b5c7c899055dd4c02971e06640dd8.poster.avif?t=1747255759\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/e80b5c7c899055dd4c02971e06640dd8.webm?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/e80b5c7c899055dd4c02971e06640dd8.mp4?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间在你手中弯曲——这是来自王的短暂恩赐——但沙漏中的沙子正悄然流逝。每走一步，街道都在改变，带来新的机遇和未知的挑战。在这款roguelite策略游戏中，你的每个选择都会掀起涟漪，带你走向未知，或让你沉沦其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/ea58aad15b8c4b0f12ba7d807756230f.avif?t=1747255759\" width=640 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>穿越时间</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助王的恩赐，你能够在战场上穿越时间。回溯过往，在梦境中施展超乎寻常的战术，打乱敌人的节奏，做出只属于梦境的不可思议的行动。现实与虚幻的边界开始模糊。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/fcf7597359d8b748fccedcefad6c9aec.poster.avif?t=1747255759\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/fcf7597359d8b748fccedcefad6c9aec.webm?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/fcf7597359d8b748fccedcefad6c9aec.mp4?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>掌握先知</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过溯回时间，你获得了无与伦比的预见力。准确预测敌人的行动，设下陷阱并利用先见之明展开连击。掌控时间流转，巧妙配合每一次攻击，破坏敌人的计划，成就自己的胜利，或让混乱降临。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/e5f6b63b7e4accba0b0b32b97012f504.poster.avif?t=1747255759\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/e5f6b63b7e4accba0b0b32b97012f504.webm?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/e5f6b63b7e4accba0b0b32b97012f504.mp4?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>梦境迷都</strong><br>在永不停息的街道上游走，每一步都带来新的遭遇与意外的发现。这里每一天看似相同，却又永远充满着变化，城市的面貌随时在你的脚步下重组。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/5144404c0f52d5be44edb9265b0b49a2.poster.avif?t=1747255759\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/5144404c0f52d5be44edb9265b0b49a2.webm?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/5144404c0f52d5be44edb9265b0b49a2.mp4?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>权衡一切</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌控你珍贵的沙子与稀有的宝石，它们既是你生死存亡的关键，也是诱惑你的陷阱。用它们推动自己前进，获得至关重要的优势，或在绝境中翻盘。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/d92293b683bbbd8be0f9d4e816a61545.poster.avif?t=1747255759\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/d92293b683bbbd8be0f9d4e816a61545.webm?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/d92293b683bbbd8be0f9d4e816a61545.mp4?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无尽可能</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次进入梦境，都是一场全新的冒险。面对神秘的战斗、超现实的遭遇、以及沐浴在黑色阳光中的诅咒之宝。下一步又会带你去往何方？只有敢于迎接挑战的人，才能揭开真相。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/075035f13cd5ca093b2e207c0f268fef.poster.avif?t=1747255759\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/075035f13cd5ca093b2e207c0f268fef.webm?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/075035f13cd5ca093b2e207c0f268fef.mp4?t=1747255759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>迷失未知</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷雾掩盖的不仅是街道，还有隐藏的答案、深藏的恐惧，甚至是你自己。无形的脚步声回荡在你周围，无法捉摸的存在低语着，挑战你去抓住这座城市不肯揭示的真相。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296330/extras/ea58aad15b8c4b0f12ba7d807756230f.avif?t=1747255759\" width=640 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入无尽的《湖》，在被时间与疯狂撕裂的迷雾中，策略是你唯一的救赎。</p>",
